<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fcfcfc;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 18px 35px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #bbbbbb;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://dnshop.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/logodnstyle.png" alt="DN shop"
        style="height: 100px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
    </div>
    <h1>Restablecer Contrasea</h1>
    <p>Hola {{name}}, recibimos una solicitud para cambiar tu contrasea. Haz clic en el botn inferior para continuar.
    </p>
    <a href="{{reset_link}}" class="btn">Cambiar Contrasea</a>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">Si no solicitaste este cambio, puedes ignorar este
      mensaje.</p>
    <div class="footer">DN shop &copy; {{year}}</div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>